snippet.title: DokeTV
snippet.description:
Hello Guys ! Welcome to my channel :)

My name is Doke and I am an Graffiti Artist and Video maker from Slovakia.

This channel runs in VLOG format however the main two topics are GRAFFITI and CUSTOM Things.
For better understanding check the PLAYLISTS :)

PS: All my activities are legal and I support just legal part of graffiti culture. People should not do ilegal stuff.

If you would like to send me something :

Martin Hirner
P.O.BOX 12
85003, Bratislava 53

Have a nice day !
